name: Barong Balinese
description: Barong Bali is one of the many varieties of Balinese performing arts. Barong is a traditional Balinese dance which is characterized by a mask and body costume that can be worn by one or two people to dance. In Bali there are several types of barong namely Barong Ket, Barong Bangkal, Barong Landung, Barong Tiger, Barong Gajah, Barong Asu, Barong Brutuk, Barong Lembu, Barong Kedingkling, Barong Kambing, and Barong Gagombrangan.
